         <abstract>
            <p>This report presents near-minimax rational approximations for the Bickley functions $Ki_1(x)$ for $x \geqslant 0, Ki_2(x)$ and $Ki_3(x)$ for $0 \leqslant x \leqslant 6$, and Ki_8(x), Ki_9(x)$ and $Ki_{10}(x)$ for $x \geqslant 6$, with relative errors ranging down to $10^{-23}$. The approximations, combined with the recurrence relation, yield a stable method of computing $Ki_n(x), n = 1, 2,\ldots, 10$, for the complete range of the argument.</p>
          </abstract>
